# Optional explicit override for the CE node base URL in a production build.
# By default the explorer uses the mesh-native, same-origin transport (the
# `window.__ceNode` bridge if present, else the same-origin `/ce` reverse proxy),
# so the strict CSP (connect-src 'self') holds and nothing off-origin is reached.
# In `npm run dev` this is unnecessary — Vite proxies /ce to 127.0.0.1:8844.
# Set this ONLY for advanced/embedded setups that need a specific node URL.
# VITE_CE_NODE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8844
